Check if a Number is Even or Odd
•	Problem: Write a C program that checks whether a given number is even or odd using an if-else statement.
•	Hint: Use the modulus operator % to determine if a number is divisible by 2.

Program
~~~~~~~

#include<stdio.h>
#include<string.h>
void main()
 {
    printf("~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~);
    printf("\n YASHWANTH KUMAR.S I-CSBS);
    printf("~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~);
     int a;
     printf("enter the number");
     scanf("%d",&a);
     if (a%2==0)
     {
         printf("even number");
     }
     else
     {
         printf("odd number");
     }
 }

Output
~~~~~~

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
YASHWANTH KUMAR.S I-CSBS
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~




